Job Responsibilities:

  Perform duties to support the monthly accounts receivable and payable closing process within the required deadline
  Check and verify payment and expenses claim
  Handle and process payments and receipts from retail outlets
  Data entry and filing of accounting documents
  Assist to process customer refund
  Handle and process petty cash of staff
  Assist and prepare monthly Gross Turnover report for all retail outlets
  Assist with month end closing
  Any other duties as assigned by the Management

Requirements:

  Candidate must possess at least Diploma/Advanced/Higher/Graduate Diploma in Finance/Accountancy/Banking or equivalent.
  At least 1&nbsp;Year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.
  Ability to prioritize while handling multiple tasks
  Meticulous, proactive, independent and good team player
  Able to work in a fast paced working environment
  Possess good interpersonal and communication skills
  Proficient in Microsoft Office such as excel, word and PowerPoint
  Knowledge in accounting software Xero is an advantage
